org.eclipse.incquery.runtime.api

Interface IncQueryEngineLifecycleListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LifecycleProvider

    public interface IncQueryEngineLifecycleListener
    Listener interface for getting notification on changes in an IncQueryEngine. You can use it to remove any other listeners that you attached to matchers or the engine, or to handle matchers that are initialized after you started using the engine.
    Author:
    Abel Hegedus
